        <h3>Benefits & Why Choose Travel Buddy</h3>
        <div class="row g-4">
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="info-card">
                    <h5>Benefits of Student Insurance</h5>
                    <ul style="color:#001f3d">
                        <li>Low-cost premiums</li>
